<item>
            <title>[LU-19139] socklnd: add separate acceptor port option for bulk transfer traffic</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19139</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add a new module parameter (e.g. acceptor_port_bulk). If specified, this port will be intended for use with bulk connections, while control connection shall be using the original acceptor_port.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The intention is to separate bulk and control traffic so that network administrators are able to apply QoS priorities based on the connection type.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
